| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0555 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4a1e7db8-bb89-5ebe-80ac-69a946bc5780"
